victory7 = "You’re so miserable that if they bring you back, the only thing you’ll achieve is dying again, more humiliated."
victory8 = "You know what you are? A bad joke even Mr. Satan would refuse to tell on stage."
victory9 = "I turned you to dust and you still smell worse than a dinosaur’s shit."


